<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA84">
<l>neṭitāya poṅkeriyun taṇmatiyu nērē</l>
<l>kaṭitāṅ kaṭuñcuṭarum pōluṅ - koṭitāka</l>
<l>viṇṭārkaṇ mummatilum ventī yiṉilaḻiyak</l>
<l>kaṇṭālu mukkaṇāṉ kaṇ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Closely he resembles to the flickering flame that is tall,</l>
<l>to the cool moon and to the fierce sun that is cruel – the eye</l>
<l>of him with three eyes, when it looks so that the three strongholds</l>
<l>of those in heaven cruelly perished in the fire.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
